com.salesforce.androidsdk.mobilesync.target

Class LayoutSyncDownTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.androidsdk.mobilesync.target.SyncTarget
      • com.salesforce.androidsdk.mobilesync.target.SyncDownTarget
        • com.salesforce.androidsdk.mobilesync.target.LayoutSyncDownTarget

  • public class LayoutSyncDownTarget
extends SyncDownTarget
    Sync down target for object layouts. This uses the '/ui-api/layout' API to fetch object layouts. The easiest way to use this sync target is through LayoutSyncManager.
    Author:
    bhariharan
